data.title: Inter Women and the athletes from Al Ittihad at Inter HQ
data.meta_description:
The meeting between Inter Women and the athletes from Al Ittihad at Inter HQ ahead of the Inter-Al Ittihad clash.
In the presence of the talented Virginia Stablum, the women met to exchange ideas and speak on their respective journeys in terms of growth and challenges in women's football, sharing about the values that have pushed them on in their careers. Before a Q&A with Nerazzurri employees, the day of "Inter Girls Chatting" kicked off with photos and a visit to the Club headquarters and trophy room.
